          "date": "2026-04-10 21:45:06.000000000",
          "tz": -360
        },
        "subject": "LU-19179 misc: cleanup checkpatch and spelling.txt",
        "message": "LU-19179 misc: cleanup checkpatch and spelling.txt\n\nRemove a large number of obsolete checks in spelling.txt that were\nadded to notify in-flight patches of changes in APIs.  Those changes\nare years old and any unlanded patches still using them cannot land\nfor many other reasons.\n\nReduce boilerplate text in prepare-commit-message so that checkpatch\nwarnings are more visible.  Otherwise they are after dozens of lines\nof text and hard to see.  With autotest running review-subtest-change\nsessions automatically, ONLY_REPEAT is not critical to mention.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@thelustrecollective.com>\nChange-Id: I79e722d0fdcb276bb55263675a1f6282cb3ebbe5\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
